Parameter:
  (<Article number/'followed-up'/'last'>)

Description:
  Writes a personal reply, i.e. a reply in the form of a mail to the
  author of the article replied.

  If the text replied to is a usenet news, a email is sent to the
  author.

  If 'followed-up' is supplied a personal reply is written to the article
  last read article was a follow-up to.

  If 'last' is supplied a personal reply is written to the article last
  read with either '(Display) next article' or '(Display) next followed-up'.

  The default is last article read.
